        </div>


        <div class="reveal">
            <div class="section-tag">
                Why Choose DivineCRM
            </div>
            <h2 class="art-h2">Why DivineCRM for Sales Follow-Ups</h2>
            <p class="art-p">DivineCRM provides:</p>
            <ul class="art-list">
                <li>Follow-up reminders</li>
